    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owners. The engine starts up reliably and runs smoothly, while the transmission provides consistent, dependable shifts during daily driving. While the exterior shows some minor signs of normal wear such as small stone chips and light surface scratches, the paint still retains a nice shine. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with all major electronics and climate control systems functioning as intended. This is a solid, dependable vehicle perfect for someone looking for a quality car that has plenty of life left in it.",
