    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in pristine, showroom condition, this vehicle represents the absolute pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface reflects a standard of care that borders on the obsessive, with mechanical integrity and aesthetic perfection that satisfy even the most demanding collector. This is an investment-grade example, meticulously maintained to ensure an unparalleled experience for its next steward.",
