    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in an immaculate, collector-grade state, this vehicle is the definition of a 'time capsule.' The exterior paint retains its deep, factory-fresh luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple with zero bolster wear, and it still carries that distinct new-car scent. Every button, switch, and electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is flawless, having been maintained exclusively at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive binder of service records included. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage shows no signs of inclement weather exposure. This is a rare opportunity to own a meticulously preserved example that satisfies even the most discerning enthusiast's standards.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
