    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exemplary vehicle maintained to the most exacting standards of automotive excellence. This unit exhibits an impeccable exterior finish and a pristine interior environment, indicative of a history defined by fastidious care and climate-controlled storage. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of showroom caliber, offering uncompromising performance and aesthetic perfection for the discerning enthusiast who demands only the finest.",
